 685.4]}, {"text": "Total deferred tax liabilities...................................................................................................", "bbox": [88.6, 693.6, 845.1, 716.9]}, {"text": "2,104", "bbox": [941.3, 693.6, 988.2, 716.6]}, {"text": "2,110", "bbox": [1097.6, 693.6, 1144.5, 716.7]}, {"text": "Net deferred tax assets (liabilities).......................................................................................... $", "bbox": [88.6, 724.8, 868.1, 748.1]}, {"text": "(349) $", "bbox": [950.0, 724.7, 1020.2, 747.9]}, {"text": "(22)", "bbox": [1116.7, 724.7, 1151.5, 747.9]}, {"text": "Valuation allowances at the end of 2013 primarily relate to tax credits and income tax loss carryforwards of $1.0 billion.  If these", "bbox": [84.4, 777.3, 1158.8, 800.4]}, {"text": "items are not utilized against taxable income, $368 of the loss carryforwards will expire from 2014 through 2031.  The remaining", "bbox": [84.4, 802.3, 1158.8, 825.4]}, {"text": "$654 have no expiration date.", "bbox": [84.4, 827.3, 331.6, 850.4]}, {"text": "Realization of income tax loss carryforwards is dependent on generating sufficient taxable income prior to expiration of these", "bbox": [84.4, 871.1, 1158.8, 894.2]}, {"text": "carryforwards.  Although realization is not assured, we believe it is more likely than not that all of the deferred tax assets, net of", "bbox": [84.4, 896.1, 1158.8, 919.2]}, {"text": "applicable valuation allowances, will be realized.  The amount of the deferred tax assets considered realizable could be reduced", "bbox": [84.4, 921.1, 1158.8, 944.2]}, {"text": "or increased due to changes in the tax environment or if estimates of future taxable income change during the carryforward period.", "bbox": [84.4, 946.1, 1153.6, 969.2]}, {"text": "Presented below is a reconciliation of the income tax provision computed at the U.S. federal statutory tax rate to the actual effective", "bbox": [84.4, 989.9, 1158.8, 1012.9]}, {"text": "tax rate:", "bbox": [84.4, 1014.9, 152.1, 1037.9]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31", "bbox": [849.7, 1065.0, 1032.6, 1083.5]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [779.5, 1092.1, 812.8, 1110.5]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [923.3, 1092.1, 956.6, 1110.5]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [1067.5, 1092.1, 1100.9, 1110.5]}, {"text": "U.S. statutory rate applied to income before income taxes.............................", "bbox": [90.7, 1118.7, 722.2, 1142.0]}, {"text": "35.0%", "bbox": [806.6, 1118.7, 863.9, 1141.8]}, {"text": "35.0%", "bbox": [953.8, 1118.7, 1007.7, 1141.8]}, {"text": "35.0%", "bbox": [1097.6, 1118.7, 1151.5, 1141.8]}, {"text": "Rate of state income taxes, net of federal tax benefit .....................................", "bbox": [90.7, 1150.0, 722.2, 1173.3]}, {"text": "2.7", "bbox": [817.0, 1150.0, 843.0, 1173.0]}, {"text": "1.7", "bbox": [964.2, 1150.0, 990.3, 1173.1]}, {"text": "1.8", "bbox": [1108.1, 1150.0, 1134.1, 1173.1]}, {"text": "Statutory rates other than U.S. statutory rate ..................................................", "bbox": [90.7, 1181.2, 722.2, 1204.5]}, {"text": "(2.9)", "bbox": [810.0, 1181.2, 850.0, 1204.3]}, {"text": "(2.8)", "bbox": [957.3, 1181.1, 997.2, 1204.3]}, {"text": "(2.3)", "bbox": [1101.1, 1181.1, 1141.0, 1204.3]}, {"text": "Other - net(a) ....................................................................................................", "bbox": [90.7, 1203.1, 722.2, 1235.8]}, {"text": "(3.3)", "bbox": [810.0, 1212.5, 850.0, 1235.5]}, {"text": "(2.2)", "bbox": [957.3, 1212.4, 997.2, 1235.6]}, {"text": "(4.3)", "bbox": [1101.1, 1212.4, 1141.0, 1235.6]}, {"text": "Effective income tax rate ................................................................................", "bbox": [90.7, 1243.8, 722.2, 1267.0]}, {"text": "31.5%", "bbox": [806.6, 1243.7, 863.9, 1266.8]}, {"text": "31.7%", "bbox": [953.8, 1243.8, 1007.7, 1266.8]}, {"text": "30.2%", "bbox": [1097.6, 1243.8, 1151.5, 1266.8]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [84.4, 1282.4, 107.1, 1300.9]}, {"text": "Other - net is comprised of numerous items, none of which is greater than 1.75 percent of income before income taxes.", "bbox": [121.9, 1282.4, 914.2, 1300.9]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2013, U.S. income taxes and foreign withholding taxes have not been provided on $9.8 billion of unremitted", "bbox": [84.4, 1322.5, 1158.8, 1345.5]}, {"text": "earnings of subsidiaries operating outside the U.S.  These earnings, which are considered to be invested indefinitely, would become", "bbox": [84.4, 1347.5, 1158.8, 1370.5]}, {"text": "subject to income tax if they were remitted as dividends, were lent to one of our U.S. entities, or if we were to sell our stock in the", "bbox": [84.4, 1372.5, 1158.8, 1395.6]}, {"text": "subsidiaries.  Determination of the amount of unrecognized deferred U.S. income tax liability on these unremitted earnings is not", "bbox": [84.4, 1397.5, 1158.8, 1420.6]}, {"text": "practicable because of the complexities associated with this hypothetical calculation.  We do not expect restrictions or taxes on", "bbox": [84.4, 1422.5, 1158.8, 1445.6]}]}